The body of the 39 year-old actor, who was presumed to have drowned, after a  fall from a waterfall, on Thursday evening  (12 April), in the Monks Cowl Nature Reserve in the Drakensberg,  has been found.  The body has not been officially identified yet, and police will be investigating an inquest into the death of the actor. ICYMI – Full story here – Actor Missing while filming in Drakensberg